iMxukugAnu prayogAlu nirvahiMceMxuku oVka eVyirkrAPtanu koVnugolu ceyAlani nirNayiMciMxi.
I teVMdarlanu julElo AhvAniswAmani keMxramaMwri harRavarxan weVlipAru.
meGAlanu aXyayanaMcesi vAwAvaraNa mArpulanu aMcanAveyadaM, BUvAwAvaraNaMloni vAyuvula laByawa vaMti aMSAlapE prayogAlu nirvahiMce puNeloni instityUt AP trApikal meVtrolajI (EEtIeVM) AXvaryaMlo.. I eVyirkrAPtanu koVnugolu ceyanunnAru.
reVMdo aMwarjAwIya yogA xinowsavAnni GanaMgA nirvahiMceMxuku keMxraM erpAtlu ceswoMxi.
iMxulo BAgaMgA keMxra praBuwva uxyogulaku yogA SikRaNa kAryakramAlu erpAtuceseMxuku xeSaMloni pramuKa yogA saMsWalu muMxukoVccAyi.
jUn 21na jarige aMwarjAwIya yogA xinowsavAnni.. anni keMxra praBuwva kAryAlayAllonU nirvahiMcAlani, uxyogulu iMxulo pAlgoVnAlani.. keMxraM spaRtamEna AxeSAlu jArIcesiMxi.
viBajiwa AMXrapraxeS rARtrAniki muKyamaMwrigA caMxrabAbunAyudu bAXyawalu cepatti reVMdelYlu pUrwayyAyi.
I saMxarBaMgA sahajaMgAne weVlaMgANa- epI muKyamaMwrula paniwIrunu, uBaya rARtrAlalo cotucesukuMtunna pariNAmAlanu prajalu berIju vesukuMtAru.
rAjakIyaMgA, pAlanaparaMgA weVlaMgANa muKyamaMwri keV.caMxraSeKararAvu distiMkRanlo pAskAgA, caMxrabAbu nAyudu saMgawi emiti? aMte eVtU ceVppaleni parisWiwi uMxi.
iMxuku AyA rARtrAlalo neVlakoVnna parisWiwule praXAna kAraNaM!
kesIArku weVlaMgANa seVMtimeVMtwopAtu mareVnno aMSAlu kalisirAgA, caMxrabAbuku kAlaM kalisirAkapogA eVnno prawibaMXakAlu eVxurayyAyi.
marovEpu keMxraM nuMci ASiMcina ceyUwa laBiMcadaM lexu kUdA!
xIMwo apAra anuBavaM unna caMxrabAbu nAyudu atu pAlanapE, itu rAjakIyAlapE pattu sAXiMcadAniki ApasopAlu paduwUMdagA kesIArku weVlaMgANalo nallerupE baMdi nadakalA vyavahArAlu sAPIgA sAgipowunnAyi.
weVlaMgANa rARtraM vaddiMcina viswarivaMtixi kAvadame iMxuku praXAna kAraNaM.
axe samayaMlo AyA prAMwAla prajala manaswawvAlu kUdA maro kAraNaMgA kanipiswoMxi.
migulu AxAyaMwo erpadina weVlaMgANa rARtra prajalu ‘mA rARtraM’ anna BAvaMwo kaxaM woVkkuwU, paxaM kalupuwU sAguwuMdagA reVveVnyU lotuwopAtu rAjaXAni kUdA leni epIlo prajalu kasigA, kalasikattugA muMxuku sAgi aBivqxXipaWaMlo payaniMcavalasiMxi poyi ‘nAkeMti’ anna XoraNiwo vyavahariswunnAru.
weVlaMgANalo aXikAra yaMwrAMgaM yAvawwU aXikAra pArtIwo paxaM kalipi sAguwuMdagA, epIlo praBuwva yaMwrAMgaM nuMci muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbunAyuduku sahAya nirAkaraNa eVxuravuwoMxi.
reVMdu rojula kriwaM attahAsaMgA jarigina weVlaMgANa rARtra AvirBAva xinowsavaM saMxarBaMgA EeeVs aXikArulu, EpIeVs aXikArula nuMci kiMxisWAyi uxyogula varaku eVMwo uwsAhaMgA pAlgoVnagA, epIlo praBuwvaM cepattina navanirmANa xIkRa moVkkubadigA jarigiMxi.
aMwoiMwo prajale uwsAhaMgA A kAryakramaMlo pAlgoVnnAru.
weVlaMgANaku ceVMxina unnawAXikArulu, jillA kaleVktarlu sEwaM AtapAtalalo munigiwelagA, epIlo unnawasWAyi aXikArulalo pattuxale koVravadiMxi.
hExarAbAxlo sWira nivAsaM erparacukunna paluvuru sIniyar aXikArulu epIki waraliveVlYladAniki sasemirA aMtunnAru.
praswuwaM epIki ketAyiMcabadina EeeVs aXikArulalo paluvuru viXileka akkada paniceswunnAru wappa manasupeVtti kAxu.
sarEna vasawulu leni amarAvawiki waraliveVlYladAniki iRtapadani koVMwamaMxi aXikArulu dipyuteRanpE keMxra sarvIsuku veVlYladAniki prayawnAlu kUdA moVxalupeVttAru.
epI sacivAlayaMlo paniceswunna uxyogulu amarAvawiki waraliveVlYladAniki mArAM ceswunnAru.
epIki ketAyiMcabadina weVlaMgANa ciruxyogi oVkaru svarARtraMlo panicese avakASaM kolpowunnAnanna bAXawo SukravAraM AwmahawyAyawnaM ceSAru.
epI sacivAlaya uxyogula manaswawvaM iMxuku pUrwi BinnaMgA uMxi.
anniMtikI sannAyi noVkkulu noVkkuwunnAru.
jIwaBawyAlu, sOkaryAla kalpana viRayaMlo weVlaMgANawo polcukuMtunna uxyogullo svarARtraM anna BAvana mAwraM kanipiMcadaM lexu.
praBuwvaMwo ceyi kalipi kaRtAlalo unna rARtrAnni aBivqxXi cesukuMxAM anna pattuxala lekuMdApoyiMxi.
ikkada oVkka viRayaM praswAviMcAli.
rARtra viBajana jarigina koVxxirojulake uBaya rARtrAlalo uxyogulaku vewana savaraNa ceyavalasi vacciMxi.
AxAyaM ibbadimubbadigA unnaMxuna weVlaMgANalo uxyogulaku 43 SAwaM PitmeVMt ivvAlani A rARtra muKyamaMwri kesIAr nirNayiMcAru.
I nirNayaM veVluvadagAne sacivAlayaMlo, jillAllo weVlaMgANa uxyogulu saMbarAlu cesukunnAru.
muKyamaMwri kesIAr ciwrapatAniki kRIrABiRekaM cesi miTAyilu paMcukunnAru.
epI viRayAniki vaswe lotubadjeVt unnappatikI weVlaMgANalo iccAru kanuka epI uxyogulu cinnabuccukorAxanna BAvanawo akkadi muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbunAyudu kUdA 43 SAwaM PitmeVMt iccAru.
nijAniki uxyoga saMGAla nAyakulu 33 SAwaM PitmeVMt iswe axe paxivelu anna BAvanawo unnAru.
ayinA 43 SAwaM laBiMciMxi.
UhiMcani viXaMgA PitmeVMt laBiMcinA epI uxyogulu saMbarAlu cesukunnaxI lexu.
muKyamaMwrini aBinaMxiMciMxI lexu.
nijAniki ixxaru muKyamaMwrulU vAri soVMwa dabbunu uxyogulaku ivvadaM lexu.
prajala dabbu uxyogulaku paMcAru.
ayinA weVlaMgANa uxyogulu kesIArnu AkASAniki eVwwagA, epI uxyogulu mAwraM eVvari kosaM iswArule annattugA vyavahariMcAru.
mOlikaMgA uBaya rARtrAla prajala manaswawvAla maXyagala wedA ixi!
weVlaMgANalo unnawAXikArulu PElYlanu parugulu peVttiswuMdagA, epIlo koVrrIlu veyadAniki iRtapaduwunnAru.
oVkkamAtalo ceVppAlaMte weVlaMgANalo aXikAra yaMwrAMgaM kiMxinuMci pEsWAyi varaku muKyamaMwri kanusEgala meraku naducukuMtU uMdagA epIlo mAwraM kulAlu, pArtIlavArIgA vidipoyiMxi.
kaRtAlalo unna rARtrAnni aBivqxXipaWaMlo payaniMpajeyAlanna wapana akkadi prajalalo uMxigAnI aXikAra yaMwrAMgaMlo mAwraM kanipiMcadaM lexu.
amarAvawiki uxyogulu waraliveVlYlakuMdA unnawAXikArule mokAlu adduwunnAraMte parisWiwi eVlA uMxo UhiMcukovaccu.
uxyogulu veVlYiwe wAmu kUdA veVlYlaka wappaxannaxi unnawAXikArula bAXa!
I nepaWyaMlo aXikAra yaMwrAMgaMwo melEna samanvayaM erparacukovadame ippudu epI muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbu muMxunna savAlYlalo praXAnamEnaxi.
gawaMlo aXikAra yaMwrAMgaMpE caMxrabAbuku pattu uMdexi.
ippudu axi koVravadiMxanI, caMxrabAbu mArku pAlana kanipiMcadaM lexanI prajalu BAviswunnAru.
iMxuku kAraNaM eVvarEnA A maccanu pogoVttukovalasina bAXyawa caMxrabAbupEne uMtuMxi.
aXikAra yaMwrAMgaM bAgowaM ilA uMte, epI samAjaM eVlA uMxo ippudu carciMcukuMxAM.
weVlaMgANa rARtrABivqxXi kosaM sabbaMda varNAlu kalisi paniceswuMdagA, epIlo mAwraM prajalu kulAlavArIgA cIlipoyAru.
epI aBivqxXiki awipeVxxa avaroXaM akkada kanipiMce kulawawvame!
I parisWiwini AsarA cesukunna rAjakIya nAyakulu kulAla kuMpatlanu mariMwa rAjeswunnAru.
xIMwo praBuwva prAXAnyAlu mAripowunnAyi.
uxAharaNaku kApulaku rijarveRan kalpiMce viRayame wIsukuMxAM.
weVlaMgANalo musliMlaku 12 SAwaM rijarveRan kalpiswAmani eVnnikalalo hAmI iccina muKyamaMwri kesIAr A xiSagA oVkka adugu kUdA veyakapoyinA reVMdelYla warvAwa kUdA eVvarU praSniMcadaM lexu.
epIlo mAwraM kApula rijarveRan viRayaMlo muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbunAyudu koVnni caryalu wIsukunnappatikI iMkeVMwa kAlaM aMtU huMkariMpulu ceswunnAru.
nijAniki xeSAniki svAwaMwyraM vaccina warvAwa kApulaku aMwoiMwo melu jaruguwoMxaMte axi ippude!
iMwakAlaM AyA rAjakIya pArtIlu kApulanu rAjakIya avasarAlake vAdukunnAyi.
kApulu ArWikaMgA veVnukabadi uMdatame kAxu- iwarawrA viRayAlalo kUdA vAriki anyAyaM jaruguwUne uMxi.
uxAharaNaku ciwra pariSrama viRayame wIsukuMxAM!
alanAti meti natulEna eVntIAr, eeVnAr sarasana nilabadagalige mahAnatullo eVsvI raMgArAvu praWamasWAnaMlo uMtAru.
pOrANika ciwrAlalone kAxu- ‘baMgArupApa, wAwAmanavadu, paMdaMti kApuraM’ vaMti ciwrAlalo eVsvI raMgArAvu natanaku kalYlu ceVmarcanivAru uMdaraMte awiSayokwi kAxu.
pOrANika pAwralaku prANaMposina eVntIArku samaujjIgA nuvvAnenA annattugA natiMci prekRakula mannanalu poVMxina natudu eVsvI raMgArAvu.
aMwati goVppa natudiki bawiki unnappudugAnI, canipoyina warvAwagAnI kanIsaM paxmaSrI vaMti biruxu kUdA xakkalexu.
Ayana kApu vargAniki ceVMxinavAdu kAvadame iMxuku praXAna kAraNaM.
nijAniki eVsvI raMgArAvu kApu anna saMgawi itIvalavaraku nAku kUdA weVliyaxu.
eVntIAr, eeVnAr vaMti natula jayaMwi, varXaMwulanu jarupukuMtunnavAru eVsvIAr jayaMwi, varXaMwulanu eVMxuku gurwupeVttukovadaM lexani ArAwIyagA Ayana kApu ani weVlisiMxi.
viciwraM emitaMte mIdiyA kUdA eVsvIAr jayaMwi, varXaMwi saMxarBaMgA prawyeka kAryakramAlu prasAraM ceyadaMgAnI, vyAsAlu pracuriMcadaMgAnI ceyadaM lexu.
ciraMjIvi vaMtivAru svaSakwiwo ciwra pariSramalo rANiMcinA eVsvIArku nyAyaM jaripiMcadAniki prayawniMcalekapoyAru.
eVsvIArku iMwa anyAyaM jaragadAniki Ayananu eVvarU pattiMcukokapovadame kAraNaM!
ippudu ‘nA jAwi’ aMtunnavAlYlu kUdA eVsvIAr guriMci mAtlAdakapovadaM vicArakaraM.
I nepaWyaMlo xaSAbxAla warvAwa kApulaku aMwoiMwo nyAyaM ceyadAniki prayawniswunnaxi caMxrabAbu praBuwvame!
kApulanu bIsIla jAbiwAlo cerce kramaMlo maMjunAWa kamiRannu niyamiMci, kAlaparimiwi viXiMcadaMwopAtu kApulanu ArXikaMgA AxukovadAnikE badjeVtlo veVyyikotla rUpAyalu ketAyiMci ruNAlu maMjUru ceswunnAru.
ayinA rAjakIya Sakwulu wama svArWaM kosaM wuni vaMti viXvaMsakara saMGatanalanu sqRtiMcAyi.
kApula viRayaMlo epI praBuwvaM wIsukunnatuvaMti nirNayAlu weVlaMgANa praBuwvaM wIsukuni uMdi uMte UrUvAdA muKyamaMwri kesIArnu kIrwiMcevAru.
Ayana ciwrapatAniki kRIrABiRekaM cesevAru.
weVlaMgANa prajalu kudumiswe paMdaga ani BAviswAru. nAyakudini nammuwAru.
brAhmaNa kArpoVreRan viRayame wIsukuMxAM.
paxavI viramaNa cesina praBuwva praXAna kAryaxarSi E.vE.Ar.kqRNArAvu coVravawo muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbunAyudu woVlisArigA brAhmaNa kArpoVreRan erpAtu ceSAru.
UhiMcani viXaMgA wamaku oVka kArpoVreRan erpAtu ayinaMxuku A rARtraMloni brAhmaNulu pattumani paximaMxi kUdA muKyamaMwrini aBinaMxiMcalekapoyAru.
axe weVlaMgANa viRayAniki vaswe epI praBuwva nirNayaM warvAwa koVxxi mAsAlaku muKyamaMwri kesIAr kUdA brAhmaNa kArpoVreRan erpAtu ceswunnattu prakatiMcAru.
A veVMtane brAhmaNa saMGAlu muMxukuvacci muKyamaMwri kesIArnu ASIrvaxiMcAyi.
Ayana ciwrapatAniki kRIrABiRekaM nirvahiMcAyi.
reVMdu rARtrAla prajala manaswawvAlanu viSleRiMcadAniki ilAMti uxaMwAlu eVnno!
weVlaMgANa Xanika rARtramEnappatikI akkadi prajallo pexale eVkkuva.
epIlo reVveVnyU lotu unnappatikI akkadi prajalalo pexalu wakkuva.
weVlaMgANawo polciwe epI prajala jIvana pramANAlu meVrugane ceVppAli.
gawaMlo perkoVnna pittakaWe ayinappatikI saMxarBaM vacciMxi kanuka maromAru ceVppukuMxAM!
axemitaMte britiRavAdu xeSaM vaxili veVlYlipowU weVlaMgANa, rAyalasIma, AMXrAku ceVMxina mugguriki mUdu wupAkulu icci veVlYlAdata!
wanaku iccina wupAkIwo weVlaMgANa vyakwi pittalanu, adavi jaMwuvulanu kAlcicaMpi poVttaniMpukunevAdata!
rAyalasImaku ceVMxina vyakwi wana vaxxanunna wupAkIwo prawyarWulanu kAlci caMpAdata!
ika AMXrA prAMwAniki ceVMxina vyakwi wana wupAkIni axxeVkicci dabbu saMpAxiMcadaM moVxalupeVttAdata!
mUdu prAMwAla prajala manaswawvAlanu vivariMcadAniki I kaWanu uxAhariswuMtAru.
ippudu muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbunAyudu, prawipakRa newa jaganmohanreVddi vyavahAra SEli viRayAniki vaxxAM.
gawaMlo woVmmixelYlapAtu muKyamaMwrigA panicesina anuBavaM unna caMxrabAbunAyudu ippudu viBajiwa AMXrapraxeSku muKyamaMwri ayina warvAwa wadabAtu, woVtrubAtu praxarSiswunnAru.
weVlaMgANa muKyamaMwri kesIAr aXikAraMloki vaccina moVxati rojunuMcI 2019lo jarige eVnnikalalo geVlavadame lakRyaMgA rAjakIyaMgA, pAlanAparaMgA nirNayAlu wIsukogA, caMxrabAbu waxviruxXaMgA vyavahariMcAru.
pArtI paggAlanu edAxipAtu vaxilesi pAlanapEna xqRtipeVttAru. akkada kUdA aXikArulawo samanvayaM cesukolekapowunnAru.
iMxuku kAraNAlu uMdavaccugAnI vAtini aXigamiMcavalasina bAXyawa Ayanaxe!
pAlanapE pattu bigiMcakapovadaMwo rARtraMlo avinIwi peVrigiMxanna BAvana erpadiMxi.
teVknAlajIni upayogiMcukuni wIsukuMtunna koVnni caryalavalla praBuwva paWakAla amalulo avinIwini cAlAvaraku niroXiMcagaluwunnAru.
ayiwe ummadi rARtrAniki muKyamaMwrigA unnappudu pAvalA panicesi muppAvalA pracAraM poVMxevAru.
ippudu parisWiwi aMxuku BinnaMgA uMxi.
paripAlana vijayavAda keMxraMgA sAgadaM, mIdiyA keMxrAlannI hExarAbAxlone uMdataMwo epIlo emi jaruguwunnaxo, emi jaragadaM lexo sarEna avagAhana erpadataM lexu.
kAraNAlu weVliyaxugAnI caMxrabAbuku EeeVs aXikArulaku maXya aMwaraM erpadiMxi.
muKyamaMwri emi ASiswunnAro aXikArulaku weVliyadaM lexu.
aXikArulu emi anukuMtunnAro muKyamaMwriki weVliyaxu.
I kAraNaMgA uBayapakRAla maXya aMwaraM peVruguwoMxi.
caMxrabAbunAyudu ippatikEnA aXikArulanu viSvAsaMloki wIsukuni vAriwo muKAmuKi mAtlAdiwe parisWiwilo mArpurAvaccu.
aXikArulu kUdA amarAvawiki veVlYladAniki moVrAyiMcakuMdA praBuwvaMwo sahakariMcadaM avasaraM.
weVlaMgANawo polciwe epIlo prawipakRaM balaMgA uMxi.
nijAniki weVlaMgANalo gawa eVnnikalalo 60 SAwaM prajalu weVlaMgANa rARtra samiwiki vyawirekaMgA otuveSAru.
ayiwe muKyamaMwri kesIAr wana caryalaxvArA ippudu 60 SAwaM prajalanu wanavEpu wippukunnAru.
epI muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbunAyudu prAraMBaMlo I xiSagA caryalevI wIsukolexu.
xIMwo prawipakRa nAyakudu xUkudu peVMcAru.
praBuwvAnni padagoVttadAniki kUdA saMsixXaMgA unnattu prakatiMcAru.
xIMwo wawvaM boXapadina caMxrabAbu ApareRan AkarRku weVrawIsi rAjakIya susWirawanu sAXiMce panilo paddAru.
vacce eVnnikala nAtiki 80 SAwaM prajalu wama pArtIwo uMdAlani wAjAgA Ayana prakatiMcAru.
kevalaM saMkRema kAryakramAlanu peVMcadaMxvArA axi sAXiMcavaccunani caMxrabAbu BAviswe axi Brame avuwuMxi.
epI prajalu aBivqxXini korukuMtunnAru.
reVMdelYlu gadicinA PalAnA prAjeVktu pUrwayiMxanigAnI, PalAnA pariSrama vacciMxanigAnI ceVppaleni parisWiwi!
viSAKapattaNaMlo EtI pariSramala parisWiwi eVkkada vesina goVMgalYi akkade annattugA uMxi.
rAjaXAni nirmANaMlo kUdA muMxadugu padavalasi uMxi.
waracugA amarAvawi nirmANaM guriMci ceVppadaM valla akkadi prajalalo aMcanAlu peVruguwuMdagA, iwara prAMwAla prajalemo muKyamaMwri wamanu nirlakRyaM ceswunnArani BAviMce parisWiwiki vaswunnAru.
prAMwAlu, kulAla maXya samawOlyaM sAXiMcavalasina bAXyawa muKyamaMwripE uMxi.
weVlaMgANalo muKyamaMwri kesIArpE akkadi prajalalo nammakaM peVragagA, epIlo caMxrabAbupE akkadi prajalalo nammakaM peVragalexu.
axe samayaMlo sadalalexu kUdA!
rARtrABivqxXi kosaM caMxrabAbu aharniSalu kqRi ceswunnAranna sAnuBUwi kUdA prajalalo uMxi.
ayiwe nAyakudipE prajalaku uMdavalasiMxi sAnuBUwi kAxu... nammakaM mAwrame!
aBivqxXi PalAlu kanipiMcanappudu prajalalo praswuwaM unna sAnuBUwi karigipowuMxi.
‘kaRtapadataM eVvariki kAvAli? PaliwaM cUpiMcAli’ ani prajalu BAviMcakamuMxe caMxrabAbunAyudu melkovAli.
kesIAr praBuwvaM muMxu miRan kAkawIya, miRan BagIraWa, sAgunIti prAjeVktula vaMti nirxiRta lakRyAlu unnattugAne caMxrabAbu praBuwvaM kUdA nirxiRta lakRyAlu peVttukuni muMxuku sAgAli.
iMxukosaM aXikArulu, uxyogulawo avagAhana erparacukuni, vAri sahakAraMwo kAryAcaraNa praNAlYika raciMcukuni amalu ceyadaM moVxalupeVttAli.
muKyamaMwri caMxrabAbulo koVnni lopAlunnappatikI epIlo Ayanaku prawyAmnAya nAyakudu lekapovadame ippatikI caMxrabAbu praXAna balaMgA uMxi.
prawipakRa nAyakudu jaganmohanreVddiki aMdagA koVnni balamEna vargAlu unnappatikI caMxrabAbuku wAnu prawyAmnAyaM ani Ayana rujuvu cesukolekapowunnAru.
rAjakIya aparipakvawa, xuMxuduku svaBAvaM kAraNaMgA I reVMdelYlalo Ayana aneka wappadadugulu veSAru.
wAjAgA ‘muKyamaMwrini ceVppuwo koVttaMdi’ ani jaganmohanreVddi cesina paruRavyAKyalu epIlo rAjakIya vAwAvaraNAnni vedeVkkiMcAyi.
Ayana uxxeSapUrvakaMgA I vyAKyalu ceSAro leka AveSaMwo annArogAnI vAtivalla Ayanaku lABaMkannA naRtame eVkkuva jarigiMxi.
poVrapAtunu savariMcukune avakASaM unnappatikI Ayana wana vyAKyalanu SukravAraM nAdu kUdA samarWiMcukovadaM AScaryaM kaligiswoMxi.
‘rAjakIyAlalo AveSaM panikirAxu’ anna prAWamika sUwrAnni kUdA jaganmohanreVddi vismariswunnAru.
nijAniki jaganmohanreVddi sWAnaMlo pariNawi ceVMxina maro nAyakudu prawipakRa newagA uMdiuMte caMxrabAbu praBuwvAnni muppuwippalu peVtti uMdevAru.
weVluguxeSaM pArtIki ceVMxina maMwrulu, iwara nAyakulu jaganmohanreVddini bayataku vimarSiswunnArugAnI, aMwaraMgikaMgA mAwraM Ayana prawipakRa nAyakudigA uMdataM wama axqRtaM ani murisipowuMtAru.
